Event-Name: Delta Sigma Pi Presents: Jeopardy at Lebow!
Description: This is a mixer-styled event where incoming Drexel freshmen can speak to several members of Delta Sigma Pi to learn more about life as a Lebow Business Student, as well as the many benefits that Delta Sigma Pi has to offer for their professional development as they navigate their budding careers. We will be playing a game of Jeopardy to get to learn more about the professional world as well as the Lebow Business School. Students will get to learn about the many renowned companies that the brothers have completed Co-ops at, as well as the companies that many alumni have worked at after graduation. We will be offering food and drinks for students to have during our event. This is a great opportunity for students to learn more about the business school and start networking with students to learn more about how to build their professional careers. This also offers a fun way to meet other like-minded peers entering the business school.
